Package com.facebook.rendercore.extensions

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExtensionsCreator
    An interface client frameworks can use to provide the list of RenderCoreExtensions to be used by the RootHost and RenderTreeHosts.
    LayoutResultVisitor<State>
    The LayoutResultVisitor API is used by RenderCore to allow a RenderCoreExtension to visit every Node.LayoutResult during every layout pass.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExtensionState<State>  
    MountExtension<Input,State>
    Mount extension which can be registered by a MountState as an extension which can override mounting behaviour.
    RenderCoreExtension<Input,State>
    The base class for all RenderCore Extensions.
